  <!--
	DESCRIPTION
  --> 
  <name>OpenChrom PDF Converter</name>
  <description>
	The OpenChrom PDF converter writes chromatogram files to PDF format. It extends the functionality of the OpenChrom Rich Client Platform (RCP).
  </description>
  <url>file:///media/3A132BBA0C9C1015/GIT-REPOSITORIES/www.openchrom.de/pdfconverter</url>
  <!--
